{"id":22022,"date":"2024-01-20T16:31:14","date_gmt":"2021-05-20T11:01:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=22022"},"modified":"2024-02-09T18:48:21","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T13:18:21","slug":"glass-wardrobe-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/glass-wardrobe-design\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Trendy Glass Wardrobe Designs For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Looking for multiple glass wardrobe designs but do not know how to go about it? We can help you with quick and easy ideas. Read along<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When thinking of a glass wardrobe for your bedroom, the first thing that comes to mind is refinement. Glass looks luxurious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While storage space is essential for a bedroom, why not cover it up with glass? Generally, wardrobe door designs with glass cover up the entire length from the ceiling to the floor; it often seems like a different room altogether that holds up your essentials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When looking for <strong>glass wardrobe designs for the bedroom<\/strong>, you will come across multiple formats on the Internet. Each one of them has a role to play that will enhance the way your room looks. Choosing one often depends on the size of the room and how you plan to dedicate space for your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobe<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few designs that work well for modern urban homes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Wardrobe Design With Mirrored Finish<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This concept seems perfect for rooms that are small and cannot accommodate a lot of furniture. When you plan to set up a glass design on the wardrobe, why not install mirrors instead? It will not just conceal your belongings but also serve as a looking glass. You do not need a separate <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/dressing-table-design\/\">dressing table<\/a> or a wall mirror to look at yourself when you get ready for the day. With bright lights, even a small room will look spacious. You do not need anything else to make your room look attractive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155923\/glass-wardrobe-design-with-mirrored-finish.jpg\" alt=\"Glass wardrobe design with mirrored finish to make your room look lavish\" class=\"wp-image-22026\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155923\/glass-wardrobe-design-with-mirrored-finish.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155923\/glass-wardrobe-design-with-mirrored-finish-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155923\/glass-wardrobe-design-with-mirrored-finish-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155923\/glass-wardrobe-design-with-mirrored-finish-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A subtle wall colour and mirrored wardrobe are sufficient to make your room look lavish<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Light And Glass Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Brightness and glass often go hand in hand as the latter reflects the light ideally to make a room look spacious. You can dedicate a particular side of your room to put up shelves for your clothing and other essentials right from the ceiling to the floor. Cover this with glass and complement it with wall lights. It could either be strip lights or bulbs that can highlight sections. You get a complete view of your wardrobe, and that saves time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155939\/light-and-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"Light and glass wardrobe design to make a room look spacious\" class=\"wp-image-22027\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155939\/light-and-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155939\/light-and-glass-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155939\/light-and-glass-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155939\/light-and-glass-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A complete view of your wardrobe without having to open it can give you that royal feeling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Frosted Glass Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While some of you may be comfortable with flaunting your wardrobe contents, others may not find it pleasant. This is when frosted glass wardrobe designs come to the rescue. With this, you get glass wardrobes as a part of your bedroom but get to hide the contents. Apart from that, frosted glass adds a hint of class to the overall look of the bedroom. It speaks for itself while giving away little. This is one of the most standard glass wardrobe designs that most people pick for their bedrooms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155902\/frosted-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"Frosted glass wardrobe design make it look perfect either way\" class=\"wp-image-22024\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155902\/frosted-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155902\/frosted-glass-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155902\/frosted-glass-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155902\/frosted-glass-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Whether the wardrobe covers an entire side or simply a particular portion of the room, frosted glass makes it look perfect either way<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Walk-In Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A walk-in wardrobe is ideal for bedrooms that are large and spacious. It could be a space where you and your partner put your clothing and other essentials that also work as a dressing room. Arranging things according to your convenience and putting glass walls to cover the shelves quickly transforms the space into a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">walk-in wardrobe<\/a>. Here, you can add a dressing area alongside a mirror and storage space for cosmetics and make-up. Some may ever replace the glass with mirrors, and that saves up on the dressing space. You can even put up lights the way you like it, especially when you want to highlight a particular section of the shoe rack or the stand where you place your bags.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155956\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-with-glass.jpg\" alt=\"A walk-in wardrobe is a dream come true for many\" class=\"wp-image-22029\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155956\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-with-glass.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155956\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-with-glass-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155956\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-with-glass-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155956\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-with-glass-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Walk-in wardrobe: putting glass walls to cover the shelves quickly transforms the space into a walk-in wardrobe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Glass Wardrobe Design That Is An Antique Setting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The presence of glass itself can transform a space and make it look mesmerising. Depending on your choice, you can either use mirrors or glass. Pastel or neutral colours help complete the space. Your modern home will be transformed with an antique wardrobe glass door design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155853\/antique-wardrobe-glass-door-design.jpg\" alt=\"Antique wardrobe glass door design for your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-22023\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155853\/antique-wardrobe-glass-door-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155853\/antique-wardrobe-glass-door-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155853\/antique-wardrobe-glass-door-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155853\/antique-wardrobe-glass-door-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding the antique touch to your bedroom with such a wardrobe can make the space look attractive<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/white-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Gorgeous White Wardrobe Designs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Playful Sliding Doors Of The Glass Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Try mixing and matching the glass on the wardrobe. Use clear glass for a portion and frosted glass for another. Allow the doors to slide when you open and close the closet. This gives a playful touch to your glass sliding wardrobe design. This will again make your room look magical.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155949\/sliding-doors-for-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding doors for glass wardrobe design\" class=\"wp-image-22028\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155949\/sliding-doors-for-glass-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155949\/sliding-doors-for-glass-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155949\/sliding-doors-for-glass-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/20155949\/sliding-doors-for-glass-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding a touch of boldness by coordinating the glass types shows how experimental you are<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While glass wardrobe designs are plenty, it needs skillful hands to help out with the execution. Once you have the experts on board, there is no looking back. You will then be a proud owner of a modern home with just the right trend being followed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-glasses\/\">Types of Glass That Amp Up Your Home\u2019s Interior<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91